rows.label: qst103609_msg0002
rows.name:
That Superbian just now!
He seemed pretty worked up
about something.

rows.label: qst103609_msg0003
rows.name:
He seemed to be heading for
the Great Stairway.

rows.label: qst103609_msg0004
rows.name:
There aren't usually many people
round there. So take care if you go!

rows.label: qst103609_msg0101
rows.name:
What would an Superbian want
around these parts?

rows.label: qst103609_msg0102
rows.name:
I hope he's not planning to
stir up any fuss...

rows.label: qst103609_msg0201
rows.name:
My curiosity got the better of me,
so I went over to the Great Stairway
myself to see what was up.

rows.label: qst103609_msg0202
rows.name:
I found that Superbian, but he
was all laid out on the ground!
So I took him to a doctor.

rows.label: qst103609_msg0203
rows.name:
No need to thank me. I wouldn't leave
anyone high and dry like that, not even
an Superbian.
